      "content": "idk, i feel okay otherwise. i mean, it's just one arm and my voice feels a little funny, but i'm not in any pain? it's probably just the cabin pressure or being dehydrated. if i just sleep for a few hours and drink some electrolytes, won't that fix it? it seems like a big overreaction to go to a hospital just for some tingling.",
